<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Multi-language translation</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
  Simply Readable supports translation into 75 languages via Amazon Translate. Try translating
  the same document into multiple languages to see how the tool handles different scripts and
  character sets.
</p>

<div class="ndx-try-this">
  <p class="govuk-body">
    <strong>Try this:</strong>
  </p>
  <ol class="govuk-list govuk-list--number">
    <li>Create a new translation of the same document, this time selecting a language with a different script (for example, Arabic, Chinese, or Hindi)</li>
    <li>Compare the output -- notice how formatting is preserved even with right-to-left text</li>
    <li>Try Welsh or Scottish Gaelic -- commonly needed by UK councils</li>
  </ol>
</div>

